        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Cooperative Management of Mineral Rights Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill repeals&nbsp;the requirement for the Forest Service to issue regulations&nbsp;regarding the development of oil and gas deposits on certain lands within the Allegheny National Forest in Pennsylvania. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
